article_title: Monsoon to Hit Northern India This Week
article_text:
MUMBAI—Monsoon rains will move into northern India over the rest of the week, the Meteorological Department said in a statement Tuesday.

After arriving over Kerala five days later than predicted, the monsoon has stalled over central India. It normally covers the entire country by mid-July, department head of long-range forecasting D. Sivananda...
